			<div class="content" id="post-content-2423457">
									

<p>Those three Tales were posted around the same time. I've always referred to them as the trifecta, and they form the canon for MC&amp;D in my head.</p>
<p>The blackboxing is because it's a Foundation transcript- everything I write is written as though it is a document that exists in a specific Foundation database.</p>

